Zork Help

This is a MUD that only does one thing: play the original Zork game.  Use
"enter portal" to start or resume your Zork session.

Useful topics:
  help commands
  help playing
  help gossip
  help account
  help version

Inside Zork, use "zork help" or "zork help <topic>" for the same files.

